{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DEVIL'S WAY 2</strong> invites players into a desolate and mysterious world for a survival challenge in this multiplayer horror and puzzle game. In the game, 4 characters face challenging questions crafted by the devil to find the right answers and escape this eerie world. Wrong answers bring terrifying and unexpected punishments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Horror Elements:</strong> Tense atmosphere, creepy environments, and events that will keep you on edge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzle-Oriented Gameplay:</strong> Solve questions correctly to progress and avoid the devil's cleverly designed traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer Experience:</strong> Play with your friends, work together to find the right answers, or succumb to fear.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Humor-Infused Storyline:</strong> Enjoy the devil's witty taunts and unexpected funny moments that will make you laugh and shiver.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmospheric Visuals and Sounds:</strong> Set in a deserted city, the game offers a dark and immersive design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In-Game Voice Chat:</strong> Communicate with your friends via in-game voice chat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Behind every door lies a new story, puzzle, and experience. <strong>DEVIL'S WAY 2</strong> combines horror and humor to deliver an unforgettable adventure. Solve the puzzles, cooperate with your team, and see if you can escape this devilish game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready, because the devil is waiting for you.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737446888","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3419120/page_b